title: Martial God Regressed to Level 2
description: Martial God Regressed to Level 2 Manhwa [Humanity, which is deemed worthless, will be deleted]. ‘Battle Net’ which was thought to be a game, turned into a disaster for humankind. After the ‘Space League’ was hosted, all living organisms in the universe fought for their lives. Humanity, represented by Earth, kept failing and was eventually annihilated. Except for one person, ‘Martial Saint’ Seong Jihan. His skill, ‘Nameless Divine Art,’ resisted the system’s deletion. Humanity, deemed worthless, received a new ‘chance’. This was the second chance granted to Seong Jihan. “This time will be different.” Since he, the one who completed the game, returned. 2레벨로 회귀한 무신 The God of War Who Regressed to Level 2 The Martial God who Regressed Back to Level 2
